    <title>通过序列构建树（中序+）</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/07/16/%E6%A0%91%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/07/16/%E6%A0%91%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA/</id>
    <published>2020-07-16T13:36:15.426Z</published>
    <updated>2020-07-20T14:21:31.505Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>树结点代码</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">node</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> data;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> layer;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">node</span>* <span class="title">lchild</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">node</span>* <span class="title">rchild</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;Bnode,*Btree;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="中序-前序"><a href="#中序-前序" class="headerlink" title="中序+前序"></a>中序+前序</h3><h4 id="思路"><a href="#思路" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h4><p>1）查找前序序列的第一个元素在中序序列中的位置，该位置将中序序列分成左子树和右子树，记录numleft；</p><p>2）继续以上面的思路迭代找到左子树/右子树的左子树/右子树</p><h4 id="要点"><a href="#要点" class="headerlink" title="要点"></a>要点</h4><p>1）迭代边界</p><p>2）创建根结点（前序序列的第一个元素）</p><p>2）个数是numleft 迭代区间长度是numleft-1</p><p>3）记得要return root</p><h4 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h4><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function">Bnode* <span class="title">createbyorder</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> preL,<span class="keyword">int</span> preR,<span class="keyword">int</span> inL,<span class="keyword">int</span> inR)</span></span>&#123;<span class="comment">//中+先 </span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(preL&gt;preR)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Bnode* root=(Bnode*)<span class="built_in">malloc</span>(<span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(Bnode));  </span><br><span class="line">root-&gt;data=pre[preL];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> k;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(k=inL;k&lt;=inR;k++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(in[k]==root-&gt;data)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;<span class="comment">//由先序根节点找到中序中根节点的位置，分出左子树和右子树 </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> numLeft=k-inL;<span class="comment">//左子树的结点数 </span></span><br><span class="line">root-&gt;lchild=createbyorder(preL+<span class="number">1</span>,preL+numLeft,inL,k<span class="number">-1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">root-&gt;rchild=createbyorder(preL+numLeft+<span class="number">1</span>,preR,k+<span class="number">1</span>,inR);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> root;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="中序-后续"><a href="#中序-后续" class="headerlink" title="中序+后续"></a>中序+后续</h3><p>1）查找后续序列的第一个元素在中序序列中的位置，该位置将中序序列分成左子树和右子树，记录numleft；</p><p>2）继续以上面的思路迭代找到左子树/右子树分别左子树/右子树</p><h4 id="要点-1"><a href="#要点-1" class="headerlink" title="要点"></a>要点</h4><p>1）迭代边界</p><p>2）创建根结点（后续序列的最后一个元素）</p><p>2）个数是numleft 迭代区间长度是numleft-1</p><p>3）记得要return root</p><h4 id="代码-1"><a href="#代码-1" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h4><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function">Bnode* <span class="title">createbypostorder</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> postL,<span class="keyword">int</span> postR,<span class="keyword">int</span> inL,<span class="keyword">int</span> inR)</span></span>&#123;<span class="comment">//中+后 </span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(postL&gt;postR)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Bnode* root=(Bnode*)<span class="built_in">malloc</span>(<span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(Bnode));</span><br><span class="line">root-&gt;data=post[postR];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> k;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> k=inL;k&lt;=inR;k++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(in[k]==root-&gt;data)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> numLeft=k-inL;</span><br><span class="line">root-&gt;lchild=createbypostorder(postL,postL+numLeft<span class="number">-1</span>,inL+numLeft,k<span class="number">-1</span>);<span class="comment">//个数是numleft 间距是numleft-1 </span></span><br><span class="line">root-&gt;rchild=createbypostorder(postL+numLeft,postR<span class="number">-1</span>,k+<span class="number">1</span>,inR);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> root; </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="中序-层序"><a href="#中序-层序" class="headerlink" title="中序+层序"></a>中序+层序</h3><h4 id="思路-1"><a href="#思路-1" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h4><p>把层序序列的第一个结点作为根结点（逻辑上就是以每层从左到右进行构建树），找到其在中序序列出现的位置，该结点的左子树和右子树就在其左右。</p><h4 id="要点-2"><a href="#要点-2" class="headerlink" title="要点"></a>要点</h4><p>1）每次是在layerL-&gt;layerR中找到第一个在中序序列中出现的结点（注意循环）</p><p>2）flag（跳出两个循环）</p><h4 id="代码-2"><a href="#代码-2" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Bnode* createbylayer(int layerL,int layerR,int inL,int inR)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">if(inL&gt;inR)return NULL;</span><br><span class="line">Bnode* root&#x3D;(Bnode*)malloc(sizeof(Bnode));</span><br><span class="line">int k,flag;</span><br><span class="line">for(;layerL&lt;&#x3D;layerR;layerL++)&#x2F;&#x2F;layer会变成后面1位或两位？减就对了 </span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">for(k&#x3D;inL;k&lt;&#x3D;inR;k++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">if(in[inL]&#x3D;&#x3D;layer[layerL])</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">flag&#x3D;1;</span><br><span class="line">break;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">if(flag&#x3D;&#x3D;1)break;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">int numLeft&#x3D;k-inL;</span><br><span class="line">root-&gt;lchild&#x3D;createbylayer(layerL+1,layerR,inL,k-1);</span><br><span class="line">root-&gt;rchild&#x3D;createbylayer(layerL+1,layerR,k+1,inR);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">return root;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
